# https://github.com/Huachao/vscode-restclient

@baseURL = http://localhost:8080

### Health Check Endpoint

GET {{baseURL}}/api/healthz

### Create a user

POST {{baseURL}}/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "mloneusk@example.co"
}

